    "enclosingSubtopic": "In the past"
   },
   {
    "text": ", and not the \"past-tense version\" of the adjective form.",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
  "In the present": [
   {
    "text": "The adjective form can be used in the present tense by adding a noun before the verb, for example, הוא כותב, ",
